The '''Suez Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] located in [[Suez]], [[Egypt]].  It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] and serves as the home stadium of [[Asmant El-Suweis]] & [[Petrojet]].  The stadium has a capacity of 27,000<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.elheddaf.com/competition/stades?competition_id=206 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2016-06-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622151456/http://www.elheddaf.com/competition/stades?competition_id=206 |archivedate=2016-06-22 |df= }}</ref> people. It opened in 1990.

